<div class="user-guide-page container">
  <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
  <p class="lead"><%= page.description %></p>

  <div class="guide-screenshot mb-4">
    <img src="<%= page.screenshotUrl %>" alt="<%= page.title %> screenshot" class="img-fluid border" />
  </div>

  <h2>Managing players</h2>
  <p>This page lists all players attached to your club. From here you can search, edit, or remove players and view their event participation.</p>

  <h3>Adding a new player</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Click <strong>Add Player</strong> (or use the <em>Add</em> button on the page).</li>
    <li>Complete the player form with name, contact details, position, and any medical or emergency contact information.</li>
    <li>Save the player record. The player will now appear on the roster and can be added to carnival teams.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Editing and removing players</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>To edit a player, click the Edit icon next to their name, update the fields, and save.</li>
    <li>To remove a player, click Remove and confirm the deletion. Removed players will no longer appear in team lists.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-3"><a href="<%= page.url %>">Open the Club Players page</a></p>
  <p><a href="/user-guide">Back to guide index</a></p>
</div>
